title: James Sturm - Sight Unseen
description:
'Sight Unseen'

Fantagraphics Books/Image Comics, 1997 & 2006, 26 pages (this is the 1997 Fantagraphics edition)

Written and Illustrated by James Sturm

Originally serialized in The Stranger and and The Philadelphia Weekly.

Mr. James Sturm is a cartoonist. He lives in White River Junction, Vermont with his wife, two daughters, a chunky little dog named Chi Chi, and two rabbits.

Besides making comics, James works at The Center for Cartoon Studies, a school for cartoonists.
